Package: discerner
Title: Ranked Preference Sorting Using Binary Insertion
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Alexi", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "alexi@example.com")
Description: Interactively rank a set of items by preference using a binary
    insertion sort algorithm. Items are sorted through pairwise comparisons,
    requiring only O(n log n) user interactions instead of comparing every pair.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    shiny
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
